  "firstAcquaintance": "A demon who loves performing magic tricks on the street. However, her work doesn't seem to go well -- she is often found collapsed by the roadside.",
  "personality": "Completely lacking the arrogance of a demon, she is passionate about performing magic tricks. She eagerly helps anyone, but because demon values differ from those of ordinary people, her help often ends up making things worse.",
  "like": "Magic tricks, apples, donating blood",
  "familiarData": "Lilith is one of the four demon generals under the Demon Lord, with unfathomable strength. However, she is casual by nature and loves performing magic tricks for passersby on the street, often being mistaken for a low-ranking lesser demon.\nA demon marquis ranked high-ranking demon can use her own blood to baptize those weaker than her, transforming other races into half-demons and making them her servants. Other races call them \"the Fallen.\" Lilith has created more Fallen than any other demon.\nBut Lilith never intended to create Fallen. She donated her blood out of a desire to help, freely giving her blood to help pitiful people become stronger and survive crises. Those baptized by demon blood will not transform into half-demons as long as they do not use the demonic power, but most cannot resist the temptation and become half-demons, resulting in many tragedies.\nBecause she has donated blood so many times, Lilith often suffers from anemia, and her strength has dropped noticeably.",
